quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,46,"Azavugisha abantu mu buhinja no mu bukwerere, kandi azaba umwe mu ntungane"
  3,47,"Aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Ni gute nagira umwana kandi nta mugabo wigeze ankoraho?\" Aravuga ati\"Uko ni ko bimeze, Allah arema icyo ashatse. Iyo aciye iteka ry’ikintu, mu by’ukuri, arakibwira ati \"Ba!\" ubwo kikaba"
  3,48,"Kandi (Allah) azamwigisha igitabo, ubushishozi, Tawurati na Injili (Ivanjili)"
  3,49,"Azanaba intumwa kuri bene Isiraheli, (ababwire) ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye mbazaniye igitangaza giturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu; ndababumbira mu cyondo ikimeze nk’inyoni, ngihuhemo maze gihinduke inyoni ku bushobozi bwa Allah. Ndakiza uwavukanye ubumuga bwo kutabona, umubembe, mbishobojwe na nzureabapfuye Allah, ndetse mbabwire ibyo mwariye n’ibyo muhunitsemu ngo zanyu\". Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ikimenyetso kuri mwe,niba koko muri abemera"
  3,50,"Kandi naje nshimangira ibyambanjirije biri muri Tawurati, no kugira ngo mbazirurire bimwe mu byo mwari mwaraziririjwe. Ndetse mbazaniye ikimenyetso giturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu. Bityo, nimutinye Allah munanyumvire"
  3,51,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Nyagasani wanjye akaba na Nyagasani wanyu; ku bw’ibyo nimumugaragire (wenyine). Iyo ni yo nzira igororotse"
  3,52,"Nuko Isa (Yesu) amaze kubatahuraho ubuhakanyi, aravuga ati \"Ni bande banshyigikira mu nzira ya Allah ? Inkoramutima (abigishwa) baravuga bati\" Twe turi abashyigikira (inzira ya) Allah, twemeye Allah,kandi unatubere umuhamya ko turi Abayisilamu (abicisha bugufi)"